---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 519
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Salvation Through Faith
By: John Smith the Platonist
---
Say not, ‘There is a lion in the way;’ say not, though religion be
good, yet it is unattainable： no, but let us intend all our powers in
a serious resolved pursuance of it, and depend upon the assistance of
heaven, which never fails those that soberly seek for it.
